[29/04/2018 21:03:04] <font color="#ffffff">¡Anda, que no!</font>
[29/04/2018 21:03:06] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Es un mono!</font>
[29/04/2018 21:03:06] <font color="#ffff00">¡Es un mono!</font>
