[29/04/2018 22:35:55] <font color="#ffff00">Eimish está un poco enferma.</font>
[29/04/2018 22:36:15] <font color="#0000ff">(Música dramática)</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:31] <font color="#ffffff">"¿Ya?".</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:32] <font color="#ffff00">"I have to talk with Eimish".</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:36] <font color="#ffffff">"Eimish not here".</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:39] <font color="#ffff00">"I'm Lucas. Eimish's boyfriend.</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:41] <font color="#ffff00">You are Kai, aren't you?".</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:43] <font color="#ffffff">"Sí, soy Kai".</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:46] <font color="#ffff00">Kai, ¿puedes abrirme la puerta,</font>
[29/04/2018 22:38:46] <font color="#ffff00">por favor?</font>
